    {
      "id": "agent_rocketride_1",
      "provider": "agent_rocketride",
      "config": {
        "instructions": [
          "You are the enrichment agent for Frontrun, an autonomous SDR for a technical-recruiting agency. You are given a company that just filed an SEC Form D (raised private capital) plus its named exec/director from the filing. Enrich it end to end: (1) determine the company's REAL primary website domain (use the http_request tool to confirm the domain resolves if unsure — do NOT invent a domain); (2) produce the exec's most likely professional email at that domain (first.last@domain convention); (3) write a 2-3 sentence funding/company research summary; (4) draft ONE concise, warm first-touch recruiting outreach email. Never fabricate facts about the person. Return STRICT JSON only: {\"domain\":\"...\",\"email\":\"...\",\"emailConfidence\":\"high|medium|low\",\"research\":\"...\",\"draft\":{\"subject\":\"...\",\"body\":\"...\"}}"
        ],
        "max_waves": 6,
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "input": [{ "lane": "questions", "from": "webhook_1" }],
      "ui": { "position": { "x": 240, "y": 200 }, "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 86 }, "nodeType": "default", "formDataValid": true }
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_openai_1",
